DTSTAMP:20260322T035031Z
DTSTART:20260403T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:The virtual meeting will be broadcast live on Zoom and recorded
	  and saved on the City Council's YouTube Channel\n\nRegistering to Speak 
	: Individuals wishing to speak live during Appearances will need to regist
	 er their request with staff at 206.275.7861 and leave a message or email 
	b efore 4 PM on the day of the Commission meeting. Each speaker will be al
	lo wed three \\(3\\) minutes to speak.\n\nJoin by Telephone at 5:00 PM: Ca
	ll 25 3.215.8782 and enter Webinar ID 825 9108 6996 and Password 896196.\n
	\nJo in by Internet at 5:00 PM:  \n\n       1\\)    Click this link\n\n   
	     2\\)    If the Zoom app is not installed on your computer\, you will 
	be prompted to download it.\n\n       3\\)    If prompted for Webinar ID\,
